arts.ttl: Julián Alvarez scores hat trick to give Atletico Madrid a 3-2 win over Rayo Vallecano
arts.sum: It was only a second league win for Atletico, which entered the match enduring one of its worst starts to a season since coach Diego Simeone took over in late 2011. Julián Alvarez scored a late winner to complete a hat trick and lead Atletico Madrid to a 3-2 victory over Rayo Vallecano in the Spanish league on Wednesday.
